{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef75018bd5","title":"六言诗·苏维埃政府布告","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"60faf69c67","index":0,"year":1931,"month":12,"day":19,"articleId":"ef75018bd5"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji5","name":"毛泽东全集第5卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji5.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cf204fd414","type":"paragraph","text":"六言诗·苏维埃政府布告","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"ef75018bd5"},{"id":"ca6ab0ba60","type":"paragraph","text":"（1931年12月19日）军同察绅地主，到处压迫穿人地主白占土地，厂主想断资本。大家要免痛苦，只有参加羊命。穷人一致备起，组织工农红军。豪绅地主土地，一律分给农民免除奇捐杂税，都是有吃有刺。工人每日工作，只做八个时辰。商人服从法令，生意由你经营。各地工农群众，赶快参加革命。建立工农政府，快把地主田分。工人组织工会，快同厂主斗争。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"ef75018bd5"}],"page":{"id":"31286b892f","publicationId":"maoquanji5","articleId":"ef75018bd5","start":475,"end":475}}}},"__N_SSG":true}